{"product_id":"the-vision-vest-ltd-ed","title":"THE VISION VEST - Ltd. Ed.","description":"\n\u003cp\u003e\"Beads work at the arm hole area\"\r\n240 GSM.\r\n100% French Terry Cotton.\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nBoxy-Fit.\r\nCombed\r\nBio-washed\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eUnleash your vision with this heavyweight 240 GSM vest, built for the bold. The front features a striking “DRIP STUDIOS” print, paired with classic streetwear art and an embossed logo for a textured, standout finish. On the back, a powerful message—“CREATOR OF MY OWN REALITY”—sets the tone for self-expression and independence. Designed with a relaxed fit and premium cotton, this vest delivers all-day comfort with undeniable presence. Whether you’re on the grind or making a statement, this piece speaks loud. Streetwear isn’t just fashion—it’s a mindset. Own yours with DRIP STUDIOS.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the t-shirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eT-shirts with 240 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46853862260890,"sku":"VEST7","price":1434.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46853862293658,"sku":"VEST7","price":1434.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853862326426,"sku":"VEST7","price":1434.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46853862359194,"sku":"VEST7","price":1434.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46853862391962,"sku":"VEST7","price":1434.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46853862424730,"sku":"VEST7","price":1434.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/IMG_6106_11zon.webp?v=1765727320","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/the-vision-vest-ltd-ed","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}